          </div>
          <dl class="mt-6 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
              <dt class="w-12 shrink-0 font-mono text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-swiss">sys</dt>
              <dd class="text-base prose-muted">your <strong class="font-semibold text-ink-900 dark:text-white">systems</strong> — data, documents and workflows, inside your walls.</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
              <dt class="w-12 shrink-0 font-mono text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-swiss">f</dt>
              <dd class="text-base prose-muted"><strong class="font-semibold text-ink-900 dark:text-white">fine-tuned</strong> — an open Swiss model tuned to them, measured before it ships.</dd>
            </div>
